  },
  {
    title: 'Walleye',
    description: 'Walleye are present throughout the lake and follow baitfish around points and ledges. Special regulations apply: all walleye from 20 to 30 inches long must be returned immediately. Daily creel limit is eight walleye, only one of which may be over 30 inches.',
